            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>¿Cómo accedemos al método <code>print_color</code> de <code>rocky</code>?</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"class\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"Dog\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"def\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"__init__\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(self)\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    self.color = \" /><text value=\"&quot;brown&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"def\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print_color\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(self)\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    print(self.color)\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"rocky = Dog()\" /></content></code><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\"><code>rocky.print_color()</code></item><item value=\"3\" correct=\"false\"><code>print_color(rocky)</code></item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>rocky.print_color()</code>.</p></body></html>"
